    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/568320/extras/fbd92dde8fa9b6d46470bedc201ac1c1.poster.avif?t=1741858031\" width=630 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/568320/extras/fbd92dde8fa9b6d46470bedc201ac1c1.webm?t=1741858031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/568320/extras/fbd92dde8fa9b6d46470bedc201ac1c1.mp4?t=1741858031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《<strong>Pictopix</strong>》是一款通过在方阵上填充方格来还原出图像的逻辑解谜游戏。游戏方式上手简单，让人欲罢不能。最初的谜题方阵较小，而到后期则逐渐变大。游戏自带300余个色彩缤纷的谜题，并有随机选关模式和谜题编辑器，一定能给您带来许多小时的娱乐！<br><br><i>这一游戏模式在英语和中文中有Picross、Nonograms、Hanjie、Pic-a-Pix、Paint by Numbers、Griddlers、数织、数墙、填方块、逻辑拼图等多种名字。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/568320/extras/d30209bca8c8e427e3d8294b2b01b227.webp?t=1741858031\" width=630 height=50 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>游玩超过300个色彩纷呈的谜题（方阵大小从5x5到40x40不等）<br></li><li>以三种不同模式进行游戏：经典、马赛克、无尽和挑战<br></li><li>自带教程，让您轻松上手<br></li><li>有众多奖章和成就供喜欢挑战的玩家获得<br></li><li>创作你自己的谜题<br></li><li>并通过Steam创意工坊和其他玩家们分享！<br></li><li>悠扬的音乐 （爵士乐与巴萨诺瓦乐）</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>其他特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>谜题从逻辑上唯一可解（不需要瞎猜）<br></li><li>拥有提示功能，适合新手游玩<br></li><li>可以用鼠标、键盘或是控制器操作<br></li><li>多个存档栏位<br></li><li>可以暂停谜题，并随时继续<br></li><li>有撤销和恢复按钮，方便玩家修正错误<br></li><li>缩放按钮，让谜题更清晰<br></li><li>可以临时标记方格<br></li><li>智能划线功能（帮助你的鼠标在划偏的情况下依旧画出直线）<br></li><li>支持触屏<br></li><li>13种语言（由社区成员协作翻译）</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特别功能</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Twitch直播功能：主播们，和观众们一起来玩吧！</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Steam特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>云存档<br></li><li>成就<br></li><li>创意工坊<br></li><li>集换式卡片</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/568320/extras/5b841a4f30f128723aedbb4eb1b0fa0a.poster.avif?t=1741858031\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/568320/extras/5b841a4f30f128723aedbb4eb1b0fa0a.webm?t=1741858031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/568320/extras/5b841a4f30f128723aedbb4eb1b0fa0a.mp4?t=1741858031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
